Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.03,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Far off into the expanse of yellow sand ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.23,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Comes great longing for a parted person ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.23,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Moonlight like water, clouds like smoke ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:09.47,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ When did it once shine down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.35,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Afraid of mortal greed abiding ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.51,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Can’t help answer your thousand words with ten thousand of mine ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:18.91,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Back then a farewell, now meeting again ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.07,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Lingering quietly grows from the fingertips ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:27.31,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Even if your ears, nose, brows, eyes can’t be forgotten ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:34.07,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Yet still wait for the two of us to have debts never more ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.43,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Gathering orchids on an empty mountain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.95,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Searching for butterflies over the sea ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.91,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Too much love and hate ultimately precludes fulfillment ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.59,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Thrilling experiences rush by ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.35,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Endlessly distant heaven and earth ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.27,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Drooping eyes are all in the past ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:47.75,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Lonely when you go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:49.15,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Yet dreams are indistinct when you return ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.19,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Perhaps this love may not be as wished ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.75,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Countless feelings overwhelm ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.67,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Heart is shaken while still young ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:58.67,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ Asking who can, by whom, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:01:59.83,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}♪ be exempt ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:07.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(640,640)}Battle Through The Heavens - Season 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:03:02.22,NEXT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,400)\pos(1792,530)}Recap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,On the Dou Qi Continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,strength reigns supreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it’s experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or forbidden arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to become stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,where have I, Mo Cheng, gone wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After swallowing the Triple Jade-Green Snake Flower Pupils,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can complete the final evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,who can still be my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it’s something from the Hall of Souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the person is found,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s about time for me to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:09.26,Episode,,0,0,0,,{\fade(640,640)\pos(960,722)}Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you are very strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,under our two Fight Emperors’ pincer attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to leave won’t be an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you return Qing Lin to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that will be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Qing Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Qing Lin is extremely important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Handing her to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Fight Emperors want to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,avoid hurting Qing Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I’m doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Old Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Heavenly Flame isn’t bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pity the way you use it is far too crude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This attack again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jia Man Empire’s maniacs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,really don’t like being reasoned with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I also don’t like being reasoned with!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Qing Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo Cheng,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you give back Qing Lin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to spare your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your so-called justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you destroyed my Mo Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ruined my plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not quite there yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly you yourself went astray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, strength reigns supreme,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,winners become king!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I am stronger than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I make the rules;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what then distinguishes right from wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You bug,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,daring to harm my Sky Serpent Mansion’s Saintess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Qing Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Qing Lin’s been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight Emperor sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Sky Serpent Mansion’s Lu Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, if I wasn’t concerned about staying too long here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and attracting Jia Ma Empire’s other strong practitioners,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,just the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,would not necessarily be my match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’d have guessed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that this filthy thing would launch a sneak attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Qing Lin’s soul has been partially sucked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I must immediately bring her back to the Sacred Pool for nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Combined with my Mansion’s Secret Technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,her soul can be fully restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,she is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Qing Lin’s soul is impaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn’t nourished and restored as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it won’t be long
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,before Qing Lin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,my Mansion’s Great Elder
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}sensed that a reincarnated Saintess possessing the Triple Jade-Green Snake Flower Pupils had appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and specially had me come welcome the Saintess back to the Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And Qing Lin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is that reincarnated Saintess I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Saintess’s aura is getting weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the Saintess to me;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise that Sky Serpent Mansion will save the Saintess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster still hasn’t died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,this monster’s strength is skyrocketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the pursuit of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he lost his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He is no longer human,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather, a beast that has lost all reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will eat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, all that monster can see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is this girl, Qing Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was snooping in the Mo Estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw records for this kind of fusion technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}It requires swallowing the intact soul of the Triple Jade-Green Snake Flower Pupils
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for this monster to complete its evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Its strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,would then be comparable to the peak of Fight Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Peak of Fight Emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Qing Lin and leave;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,fully recover her health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,allow us to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Serpent Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,wishes more than anyone for Qing Lin to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if a single hair on Qing Lin’s body is harmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will settle things with the Sky Serpent Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,he’s too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heavenly Flame can’t get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,freeze him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Lotus Core Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With this Heavenly Flame’s power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,even a Fight Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,would be gravely wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, this kid actually has two kinds of Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Hai,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m counting on you to hold back this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a way of dealing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever attack it is, use it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t hold on much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One kind of Heavenly Flame’s power isn’t enough;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then how about two kinds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually want to merge two kinds of Heavenly Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is simply unable to withstand the Heavenly Flames’ violent energy;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is like burning yourself from playing with fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Merging Heavenly Flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This fellow has gone insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if you die, who will refine the Spiritual Recovery Purple Pill for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,stabilize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you go on like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your body will fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I need more power;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,only this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t be slighted by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Only this way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,can I protect
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,those I care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you insist in such a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,stabilize your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the seed formed from merging two kinds of Heavenly Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So it’s like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dou Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lead to the same path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This terrifying power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two kinds of Heavenly Flames combined,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are always full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this have a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will call it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry Buddha Fire Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll let you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,test its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry Buddha Fire Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With my current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is this the end..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My Angry Buddha Fire Lotus succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angry Buddha Fire Lotus’s destructive power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,even I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,would be amazed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Teacher can no longer be by your side in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you now possess the capital to overcome strong enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,has been thanks to your nurturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher’s strength, paired with my Angry Buddha Fire Lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,can definitely rule the world in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angry Buddha Fire Lotus you invented,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher is quite satisfied with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, with my body’s current condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m afraid I can no longer maintain my spiritual state.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I must fall into a slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher is very happy to have you as my disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can transfer Dou Qi to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly child,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher won’t be able to continue protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you will have to rely on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry Buddha Fire Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be because I forcefully used the Angry Buddha Fire Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me that harmed Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In only thinking about pursuing strength
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I neglected the person I should’ve cared most for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the use
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of wanting all this power?
